<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4930441>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURES 2–5. 2) Holotype of Hedychrum metallicum Dahlbom, 1854 (= Holopyga metallica (Dahlbom, 1854)). 3) Lectotype of Hedychrum cupreum Dahlbom, 1845 (= Hedychridium cupreum (Dahlbom, 1845)). 4) Lectotype of Chrysis succincta var. virideocincta Trautmann, 1927 (= Chrysis bicolor Lepeletier de Saint Fargeau, 1806). 5) Holotype of Chrysis succincta var. westerlundi Trautmann, 1927 (= Chrysis westerlundi Trautmann, 1927). Scale 1 mm. Photos: Paolo Rosa (3) and Pekka Malinen (2, 4–5)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4930441/files/figure.png" .

